Olivo/bacteriosis

olivo %>%  # dataset wide (planilla de campo, con 30 columnas de sev por arbol individual)
  # le pedimos que apile las columnas conteniendo a las plantas 1 a 30
  pivot_longer(cols = `1`:`30`, 
  # el nombre de las columnas las apile en una columna llamada "tree"
         names_to = "tree",
  # la observaciones de severidad las apile en una columna llamada sev
         values_to = "sev") -> oli_long # el producto de este re-arreglo se llamar "oli_long"

oli_inc <- oli_long %>%
  mutate(diseased = sev>0) %>% 
  group_by(year, loc, farm) %>%
  summarise(inc = mean(diseased, na.rm=TRUE)*100) %>% 
  ungroup %>% 
  arrange(loc, year)

  geom_point() +
  # geom_line() +
  geom_line(aes(group=farm)) +
  facet_grid(. ~ loc)

Prevalencia (nivel regin - evolucin interanual)

oli_prev  <- oli_inc %>%
  mutate(diseased_farm = inc>0) %>% 
  group_by(year, loc) %>%
  summarise(prev = mean(diseased_farm, na.rm=TRUE)*100) %>% 
  ungroup %>% 
  arrange(loc,year)

Severidad

oli_long %>% 
  # filter(year==2015, loc=="Chilecito", farm==2) 
  group_by(year, loc, farm) %>%
  summarise(
    n = sum(!is.na(sev)),
    # inc = mean(sev>0, na.rm=TRUE)*100,
    sev_cond = mean(sev[which(!is.na(sev) > 0)]),
    sev_media = mean(sev, na.rm=TRUE)
    ) %>% 
  ungroup %>% 
  arrange(loc, year) -> oli_sev
oli_sev %>% 
  ggplot()+
  aes(x=loc, y =sev_media)+
  geom_point(alpha=.3)+
  facet_wrap("year")+ 
  stat_summary(fun = mean, geom = "crossbar", col="blue")+
  stat_summary(aes(label=round(..y..,1)), 
               fun=mean, 
               geom="text", size=4, vjust = -0.5)  +
  scale_x_discrete(guide = guide_axis(n.dodge = 2)) 

cebada %>% 
  pivot_longer(
    cols = contains("_"), 
    names_to="var",
    values_to='val') %>% 
  separate(var, c('enf', 'metric'), 
           sep = '_', convert = TRUE)->long  

long %>%
